  Product Overview
  Make short work of laundry days with this white condenser tumble dryer from Beko. Its 7kg drum makes it a great choice for busy, medium-sized households. Clever&nbsp;
    sensor drying technology works out how much moisture is in your laundry and then automatically adjusts the setting to suit, so you’ll only ever use the perfect amount of energy. The&nbsp;
    anti-crease programme will gently spin the drum to prevent wrinkles in clothing – taking the hard work out of ironing. It also has an auto cool-down phase which blows cool air into the drum at the end of the cycle, so your clothes won’t be too hot when you unload them.
  
  Heat pump tumble dryers are super-efficient, but to save the most energy, programmes may take a little longer to dry your clothes than on standard dryers. It’s important not to overload the drum either, so they can perform at their best.

