The Hoover HMCL5172WKN 55cm white 50/50 low frost fridge freezer will effortlessly store all your food thanks to its very spacious storage design. You can also reduce your utility bills and impact to the environment, thanks to the F energy efficiency rating.
Roomy Fridge Design
Located at the top is the 153-litre fridge capacity that is split between two adjustable glass shelves, a salad bin and two-door balconies for versatile storage options. The salad drawer is perfect to keep your healthy vegetables fresher for longer to mitigate your food waste.
The balconies provide additional space to hold your favourite bottled drinks. Additionally, it is great for kitchens with limited space, reversible door hinges mean the doors can be opened on whichever side you prefer &ndash; while the integrated handle gives the fridge freezer a contemporary, minimal look.
Low Frost Freezer
Fitted underneath is the spacious 100-litre freezer with four clear drawers that provide a versatile storage option for all your favourite freezer goodies. Its clear design means you can easily keep track of what you need next for your grocery.
The Hoover HMCL5172WKN comes with a low frost function which will make manually defrosting less of a chore, so you can say goodbye to wasting lots of time waiting to defrost. This prevents ice crystals from forming which could potentially damage your food items and add more food waste.
Whether you're looking to replace your old fridge freezer or furnishing a new home, the Hoover HMCL5172WKN 55cm white 50/50 low frost fridge freezer will have no trouble tackling all your storage needs, thanks to its range of innovative features.
